@NODE "Mail.65" "Score display"
From: Jake Frederick <gonzo@acadia.net>
Date: Tue, 10 Jan 1978 11:39:33 +0500
Subject: Score display

The game I am making requires two displays on one screen, a scrolling
playfield and score display. What is the best way to do this in an OS friendly
way? Should I put one on the screen and one in a window, both in a winow, or
both on the screen?
