@NODE "Mail.73" "Questions"
From: "Oliver Marks" <oly@enterprise.net>
Date: 22 Jul 98 19:37:32 +0000
Subject: Questions

Hi,

1. How can i use a asl screen mode requestor to open a screen the
manual does not tell you what the enable_flags are.

2. is it possible to hillight text in blitz which is printed in a
window so that i could make up cut copy and paste functions.

3. how do you get the little buttons that are normally next to a text
gadget that bring up a file requestor or a path requestor they are
normally square with a little picture in them.



@ENDNODE
@NODE "Mail.74" "Questions"
Date: 25 Jul 98 16:35:22 GMT
X-Plug: Xenolink, No. 1 BBS Software for the Amiga!
From: bml@darkside.demon.co.uk (Simon Archer)
Subject: Questions

On 22 Jul 98 Oliver Marks wrote about 'Questions'.

 OM> 3. how do you get the little buttons that are normally next to a text
 OM> gadget that bring up a file requestor or a path requestor they are
 OM> normally square with a little picture in them.

These are known as 'GetFile' gadgets and BlitzGUIGen will create them for you.

Simon Archer




