Somes will come as soon as I can :))

I tried to coded from the easiest example to more complexes one 'cuz it's
could be hard to understand for some users... please be patient... more very
useful and complexes codes will come... :)))

When all 12 parts will be done... and understand... everybody will be able to
code very fast program in Blitz...

Enjoy those Examples and I hope this will help you in your on develpment...
Roger


   

