ly
closed when the program ends. You can use the debugger in parallell with =
the
new library set. Great.

    ASL library is now fully supported. Much better than the old Acid lib=
=2E
Chunky library is updated and a system friendly C2P is provided. You can =
blit
your chunky buffer into a window ! An example is provided. A Font library=
 is
now available. Very easy to use :-). More examples too. Check it !

    Any suggestions, bugs report and more to my email...

    For now,

        Fred.

PS: I've spend my time to optimize these libs :-). ASM is great for
optimizing...
