@NODE "Mail.133" "NewLibraries"
From: Andreas Etzrodt <the_shark@gmx.de>
Date: Wed, 22 Jul 1998 19:15:52 +0100
X-SenderInfo: 1; address="Hauptstr. 15"; city="49835 Wietmarschen-Lohne";
   country="Niedersachsen/Deutschland"; phone="05908/714"; dob=5081975
Subject: NewLibraries

Hello,

am I wrong when I say that the NewLibrarySet
(or its lib#) collides with BSS?

Window lib collides with RInonvolatile lib (35)
Screen lib collides with RIfastserial lib (36)
String lib collides with RIgtmenu lib (37)

It there something I can do for this?

Bye, 
 Andy
