To see the rest, you will need to upgrade your mail reader.


--BOUNDARY.1748063184.2


    Hi Blitzers,

    The NewCommandsSet series continue and now the GadTools library is
supported ! Menus/Gadgets are easy to create and the result is impressive=
=2E You
can expect an under 6kb exec for a fully gadtools guided software. =


    A nasty bug in the Chunky library has been removed and a new library =
(C2P)
which contain the famous 040 optimized C2P has been created. A new exampl=
e to
handle chunky gfx is present.

    If anyone can test these new commands and send me their remarks on it=
, it
could be great. I'd like to mean that this project could give the Blitz 3=
=2E
I've very motivated by doing that but I need some help... English isn't m=
y
native langage and writing a guide for the commands I code take lot of ti=
me. I
spend almost the same amount of time to develop the libs and to write the=
ir
docs !

    the guide format has been changed and its become very modular. i thin=
k
this could be a good start for a new Blitz 2 manual... If somebody is
interrested...

     Regards,

            Fred.

