@NODE "Mail.139" "New Wreckage (XV44.1)"
	id 0ywPJl-0001Fq-00; Wed, 15 Jul 1998 12:01:49 +0100
From: C Dimitrakakis <cdimita@essex.ac.uk>
Subject: New Wreckage (XV44.1)
Date: Wed, 15 Jul 1998 12:02:15 +0100 (British Summer Time)
X-Authentication: IMSP

A new version of wreckage is now available at my homepage

http://esewww.essex.ac.uk/~cdimita

and on aminet, shortly

Please check it out and give me your comments


History:
-------

Experimental Revision 44.1
--------------------------
Landscape now Shaded
16 colours in hi-colour mode


Experimental Revision 44 
------------------------

Landscape now visible.
Lansdscape parameters adjustable.
Road follows landscape (adjustable).

Slightly improved sound.

Fine-tuned static/dynamic friction characteristic.
Brakes and brake fluids can overheat.
Engine Power/Torque curves more realistic (and different for each car).

Easy Driving Option Added (simplifies friction characteristic)
Added more camera views.
Gravity now adjustable.
Added Manual Gears and Rev-Meter.
More steering options added.
Improved look of car slightly.
Minor bugs fixed.


Experimental Revision 43
------------------------
Added hills.
Expanded simulation model for correct behaviour on slopes.
Power now not linearly increasing with revs.

Experimental Revision 42b (fast)
--------------------------------
Now 68030+ ONLY
===============
Major Crash-Bug removed
